<HEAD>TV's `Hawk' Series Begins Filming In Capital</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Prime time television is coming to the nation's
capital with the advent of the ``Hawk'' series, a spinoff of the
departed ``Spenser: For Hire'' program.
   The action-drama show, starring Avery Brooks, is the first series
ever filmed in and around Washington, D.C. It will be aired by ABC
